<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Technical Support</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/main.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="menu">
            @if (User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
            {
                @if (User.IsInRole("Executor") || User.IsInRole("Admin"))
                {
                    <a href="/Executor/ExecutorPrivatePage">Задачи</a>
                }
                @if (User.IsInRole("Customer") || User.IsInRole("Admin"))
                {
                    <a href="/User/UserPrivatePage">Мои задачи</a>
                }
                <div class="logout">
                    <form color="white" method="post" asp-controller="Login" asp-action="Logout">
                        <input type="submit" value="Выход" />
                    </form>
                </div>
            }
            else
            {
                <a href="/Login/LogIn">Войти</a>
                <a href="/Registration/Registration">Зарегистрироваться</a>
            }
        </div>
    </header>
<div class="content">
    <div class="menu-text">
        <p>Техническая поддержка<br /></p>
        <h7>Любые ваши задачи<br /></h7>
        <h8>В любое время</h8>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>